entries.femaleVariant: Thought they'd rampage as soon as we swooped onto their turf.
Thought Watchers always worked as, uh… couples.
Huh, thought they were on their own, independent.
But there's fuck all here in the GIM.
Right? No control over your own turf.
Pathetic. 'Squatch would never let that slide.
This one's a hunter, works solo.
So, what? He gettin' paid for every Voodoo brain he roasts?
Not this time. Killin' jujus on the side's just a bonus. He's here to trash the Voodoos' subnet.
Think of it like someone rippin' out your body mods.
You'd be a helpless fuckin' worm. That's what he wants – to make 'em squirm.
Who'd feed their wallets, then? Grateful people of the world?
But that's like a shared interest, right? Keepin' the Net clean?
Listen, only corps do biz on the Net. NetWatch would be dead without 'em.
